Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,御主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不可以碰到黑泥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我的冥界竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼速度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是麻煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒 你跟藤丸去阻止Beast鑽出地面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,包 包在我身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只有兩隻的話根本不成問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,這個拉赫穆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就是新型的「十一個孩子」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,總之我們先牽制住他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好 如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,怎能讓你們得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真是好纏人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,得想辦法擋下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.41,0:06:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這下真的不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,這力量 是神靈級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.59,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這句話 之前就想說一次看看了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.06,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.35,0:07:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,既然如此 就拿出看家本領吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,雖說這不符合我的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,當年竟然能憑這個讓那個阿爾托莉亞上鉤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是提亞馬特神真正的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,每個都足以跟魔神的首領匹敵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,糟了 已經能看到地上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,用我的寶具來絆住她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪修
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的冥界裡 你別想為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Beast就會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你們在那裡慢慢吞吞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,由本王來助你們一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,從者 Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,英雄王吉爾伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,本王看不下去 才會特地來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.96,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 這副模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾伽美什王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不 是從者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,他該不會是自力現界的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,別鬆懈 不可以分散注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,這個反應是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會 該不會是固有結界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,世界新生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,反創世紀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Latina,,0,0,0,,Nega Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.93,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Nega Genesis{\r};[英語]對創世紀的否定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.82,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,天有絕海 地有監獄
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,吾之踵乃冥界之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,出現吧 發熱神殿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1100,1300,\3c&H81D8FF&\blur15)\fad(0,500)}靈峰踏抱冥界之鞴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1100,1300,\3c&H81D8FF&\blur15)\fad(0,500)}Kur Kigal Irkalla
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:38.21,EXComments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Kur Kigal Irkalla{\r}:[蘇美語]{\rUr3}𒆳  𒆠𒃲  𒅕𒆗𒆷{\r},「山脈之基為冥界」\N在古蘇美傳說中,冥界的入口位於扎格洛斯山脈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,停下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:11:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,封印Beast了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,內爾伽勒賜予的神殿具現化嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:03.91,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\pos(690,990)}Nergal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:04.57,EXComments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Nergal{\r}(內爾伽勒):[蘇美語]{\rUr3}𒀭𒄊𒀕𒃲{\r}({\rTra}ᵈGIR-UNUG-GAL{\r}),埃列什基伽勒的丈夫.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,確實適合拿來當殺手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.33,0:12:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很不甘心這只能拿來爭取時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那個空間肯定還會再嘗試用侵蝕逃脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,梅林 反創世紀是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.59,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那傢伙 打算塗改整個冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,塗改
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,被那個以Beast為核心擴散開來的空間吞噬之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,所有的從者都會被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會有這麼不像話的權能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要跟那個不祥的結界對抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,必須借用你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,某位王思念的白堊之壁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只要讓它顯現 或許就能與之抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,要用瑪修的「已然遙遠的理想之城」整個撞上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就算這樣能抵擋擴散
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.42,0:13:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,在瑪修拚命努力的期間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要有人給Beast最後一擊才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 能做到這點的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,反創世紀是否定既有的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,企圖誕生出新生命的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 那個空間只能允許生者存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在發動寶具期間她無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這個你拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄準頭部 那裡就是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.50,0:13:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 在那空間裡我的特權就沒效了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟瑪修一起同時使用寶具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.34,0:13:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,為你鋪路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,御主 我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,瑪修
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:13:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你只要面向前方使盡全力就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,之後的事情就全部交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你 御主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,結界已經快要撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,星之內海 瞭望之台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,真名 公開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我立於災厄之席
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,從樂園的角落告知汝等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,汝等的故事充滿了祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.76,0:14:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只有無罪之人可以進入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那是能治癒所有傷痕 所有怨恨的吾等故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,顯現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(2000,2500,\3c&HF7FF74&\blur15)\fad(0,300}已然遙遠的理想之城
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.90,0:14:48.36,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(2000,2500,\3c&HF7FF74&\blur15)\fad(0,300}Lord Camelot
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1500,2500,\3c&HE9E3FF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}永世隔絕的理想鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1500,2500,\3c&HE9E3FF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}Garden of Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:57.37,Comments,,0,0,0,,{\rLatina\fs40}Garden of Avalon{\r}:「理想鄉的庭院」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我就覺得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,打破冥界的禁忌 出借力量給生者之後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.40,0:15:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,使用了這麼多的權能 怎麼可能會沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.07,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是冥界的女主人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,只是為了守護冥界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,用了一個 最有可能成功的方法而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.33,0:15:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你好不容易才認識了能溝通的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果現在的你消失了那還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,下次會不會有更戲劇化的 相遇方式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我的基本神性 比現在還要陰沉一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(830,990)\fs35}性格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,可能沒辦法順利說上話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.94,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不是喜歡現在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,而是很欣賞那個人類的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,埃列什基伽勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的冥界裡有那麼多花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.27,0:17:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,既然是一群死者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,由死亡來當你們的對手 也是理所當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我接受掃蕩敵人的委託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你就作為生者向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,都走到這一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.63,0:19:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吉爾伽美什
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.26,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看來分出勝負了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.55,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,藤丸立香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,本王就拿這一擊當作餞別禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,敘述原初 開天闢地之時 虛無亦為此獻上祝賀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,以吾之乖離劍撕裂世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,環繞眾星之臼 天上的地獄乃創世前夜的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,以你的死來平息一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,2100,\3c&H002BFF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}天地乖離開闢之星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.30,0:20:01.26,Latina,,0,0,0,,{\t(1800,2100,\3c&H002BFF&\blur15)\fad(0,300)}Enuma Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.37,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,孕育了無數的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,被無數的生命所敬愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.87,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.08,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子們將我當作階梯 離我遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想要愛他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想留在他們身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我的愛 是不是錯誤的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 孩子們都是愛著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我必須要離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要丟下我離去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再愛我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:23.44,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏み込んだshadowland 楽園なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 確信なんてない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}それでも go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.04,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}しがみつく became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}涙にさえ灯る日が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}ひとつのsign ひとつのlight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:47.92,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}明けない夜も 歌が途切れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:53.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}当てなく迷う夢が縺れないように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.69,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}すれ違った足跡達 振り返らぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏み外したあなたでさえ 手放さないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover I am the prover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:18.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}終らない世界にだって立ち向かうように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:24.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 命の声がまた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.93,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}響きだす頃に あなたと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:36.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}沈まずに行く船を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.35,0:22:23.44,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}踏入shadow land 才不是樂園
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.70,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}Sappy old remedies 無法確定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:31.87,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}即使如此 go up the river
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:35.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}咬緊牙關 became a ladder
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.12,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}連有眼涙都宛如燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.12,0:22:41.88,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}一個sign 一個light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.88,0:22:47.92,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願沒有黎明的夜晚 歌聲不會間斷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:53.51,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願不要困在和彷徨迷惑的夢境裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:59.69,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願交錯的足跡們不再執著過去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:06.11,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願就算你一旦失足 也千萬別放手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.95,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover I am the prover
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:18.46,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}但願能勇敢面對沒有結束的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:24.29,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}I'm the prover 生命的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.29,0:23:30.93,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}還在發出聲響 與你一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:36.77,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(500,500)}駛著的船隻 不讓它沉沒
